@startuml
title System/Backend Sequence Diagram

participant "Firebase Authentication" as Auth
participant "Firestore" as DB
participant "Cloud Functions" as CF
participant "Firebase Storage" as Storage
participant "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM
participant "Emergency Contacts" as Contacts
participant "Expo App" as App

== Authentication & Role Assignment ==
Auth -> DB : Validate user
activate Auth
activate DB
DB --> Auth : Role (User/Admin)
deactivate DB
Auth --> App : Access token
deactivate Auth

== Disaster Report Handling ==
App -> DB : Submit disaster report
activate DB
DB -> CF : New report trigger
activate CF
CF -> DB : Set status = Pending
CF -> FCM : Notify nearby users
activate FCM
deactivate FCM
deactivate CF
deactivate DB

== Media Association ==
App -> Storage : Upload media
activate Storage
Storage --> DB : Save media URL
activate DB
deactivate DB
deactivate Storage

== Voting & Verification Logic ==
App -> DB : Submit vote
activate DB
DB -> CF : Vote update trigger
activate CF
CF -> CF : Check vote threshold
CF -> DB : Update verification status
CF -> FCM : Notify users & admin
activate FCM
deactivate FCM
deactivate CF
deactivate DB

== Admin Overrides ==
DB -> CF : Admin status update
activate CF
CF -> FCM : Broadcast status change
activate FCM
deactivate FCM
deactivate CF

== SOS Automation ==
App -> DB : Store SOS alert
activate DB
DB -> CF : SOS trigger
activate CF
CF -> Contacts : Send emergency alerts
activate Contacts
CF -> FCM : Notify admin
activate FCM
deactivate FCM
deactivate Contacts
deactivate CF
deactivate DB

== Data Cleanup ==
DB -> CF : Report/media deletion
activate CF
CF -> Storage : Remove media
activate Storage
CF -> DB : Update references
deactivate Storage
deactivate CF

== Real-Time Sync ==
DB --> App : Live updates
activate DB
deactivate DB

@enduml
